15

Plaintiffs will serve Defendants with formal discovery requests on these subjects. During

16 the period of expedited discovery, Defendants shall have seven days from the date of service to

17 object to the States’ discovery requests, and 14 days from the date of service to respond to
18 requests for production, interrogatories, and requests for admission. Defendants will expedite
19 the production of responsive information and documents, and will confer with Plaintiffs as to
20
21 any questions regarding the scope and meaning of the requests.

22

